=Signs=
Flea bites will appear as clustered or appear in a 'line' of separate bites, and the resulting bumps are itchy yet smaller than mosquito bites.
==Controlling Fleas==
Citrus oils, eucalyptus and neem oils mixed with water and applied to sheets will repel fleas.

